section.para:
The paginator component needs a service(
) to provide true pagination so basically 
to create a  paginator will'll setup its service and you can do this by the following ways:

listitem.programlisting:

                public void initPaginator() {
    // paginator needs a service to access DB and perform
    // true pagination, sort and filtering over a collection
    paginator = new Paginator(aService);
}
